== Datamodel
	 We will later use the following datamodel for the example.
	
	 Create a Java project "de.vogella.spring.di.model" and create
		the following packages and classes.
	
[source,java]
----
include::res/datamodel/IWriter.java[]
----
	
	
[source,java]
----
include::res/datamodel/Writer.java[]
----
	
	
[source,java]
----
include::res/datamodel/NiceWriter.java[]
----
	
	
[source,java]
----
include::res/datamodel/MySpringBeanWithDependency.java[]
----
	
	 The class "MySpringBeanWithDependency.java" contains a setter
		for the actual writer. We will use the Spring Framework to inject the
		correct writer into this class.
